jñānānandamayaṃ devaṃ nirmalasphaṭikākṛtim|
ādhāraṃ sarvavidyānāṃ hayagrīvamupāsmahe||}
khagāsanaṃ [2]ghṛṇādhāramīdṛśaṃ somabhūṣitam|
akalaṅkendusūryāgniṃ lakṣmīrūpamupāsmahe || 2 ||
