52. saptatyeti| śuddhāśuddhādhvanoḥ pratyekaṃ pañcatriṃśaditi āhatya saptatirbhedāḥ| ī śaktiḥ; īkārarūpā śaktirityarthaḥ|
{15}iyadvistṛtimāpannāmīmimāṃ parameśvarīm|
